---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import About from '../components/About.astro';
import Skills from '../components/Skills.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="David Manjarres | Full Stack Developer - Java, Spring Boot, React">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <Hero />
    <hr />
    <About />
    <hr />
    <Skills />
    <hr />
    
    <section class="education" id="education">
      <h2>My <span class="enfasis-title">Education</span> & <span class="enfasis-title">Certificates</span></h2>
      <p><i>Education is not the learning of facts, but the training of the mind to think.</i></p>
      <div class="education-grid">
        <article class="university">
          <div class="institute-img"><img src="/assets/img/uta.jpg" alt="Universidad Técnica de Ambato" /></div>
          <div class="institute-description">
            <h3><a href="https://www.uta.edu.ec/v4.0/" target="_blank">Universidad Técnica de Ambato</a></h3>
            <p>Software Engineering</p><p>2021 - Now</p>
            <p>During my time at the Universidad Técnica de Ambato, I have gained a solid foundation in software development, including programming, algorithms, and system design. I have also participated in various projects that have honed my problem-solving and teamwork skills.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="certificates">
          <div class="institute-img"><img src="https://img-c.udemycdn.com/course/240x135/5241962_0546.jpg" alt="GraphQL and Node.js" /></div>
          <div class="institute-description">
            <h3><a href="https://www.udemy.com/certificate/UC-c05cdc6d-e2c7-45cd-baec-2c64499f6ca7/" target="_blank">GraphQL and Node.js: Modern and efficient applications</a></h3>
            <p>Udemy - 2024</p>
            <p>This course provided me with advanced skills in building modern and efficient applications using GraphQL and Node.js. I learned how to design scalable APIs and integrate them with front-end frameworks.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="certificates">
          <div class="institute-img"><img src="https://img-c.udemycdn.com/course/240x135/4813286_d96b_4.jpg" alt="FullStack and Desktop Programming" /></div>
          <div class="institute-description">
            <h3><a href="https://www.udemy.com/certificate/UC-4cf24303-9098-4a60-9787-adf82c453a46/" target="_blank">FullStack and Desktop Programming from ZERO to PROFESSIONAL</a></h3>
            <p>Udemy - 2022</p>
            <p>In this course, I mastered full-stack development, from front-end technologies like HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to back-end frameworks like Node.js and databases. I also gained experience in desktop application development.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="full-width">
          <div class="institute-img">
            <div class="image-container">
              <img src="https://cdn.efset.org/efset-widget/img/v2/social-media/certificate/cefr-badge-B2.svg" alt="EF SET Certificate" />
              <img class="badge-logo" src="https://a.storyblok.com/f/246158/103x24/eb1cf2418f/efset-logo_white.svg" alt="EF SET Logo" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="institute-description">
            <h3><a href="https://cert.efset.org/vmT4Vg" target="_blank">B2 Upper Intermediate</a></h3>
            <p>EF SET - 2025</p>
            <p>This certification demonstrates my proficiency in English at the B2 level, enabling me to communicate effectively in professional and academic environments.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
    <hr />
    
    <section class="projects" id="projects">
      <h2>My <span class="enfasis-title">Projects</span></h2>
      <div class="projects-grid">
        <article class="project">
          <div class="project-image"><img src="/assets/img/amazon.png" alt="E-Commerce Marketplace Platform" /></div>
          <div class="project-content">
            <h3>E-Commerce Marketplace Platform</h3>
            <p>Complete marketplace serving <strong>5,000+ users</strong> with Spring Boot backend and React/TypeScript frontend. Features RESTful APIs with JWT/RBAC security, pagination, and content moderation. Achieved <strong>85% response time improvement</strong> (300ms → 45ms) through Redis multi-layer caching and database optimization. Deployed with CI/CD using Jenkins, SonarQube, and Azure Container Apps with <strong>90% test coverage</strong> and 95+ Lighthouse score.</p>
            <div class="technologies">
              <span><i class="devicon-spring-original colored"></i> Spring Boot</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-postgresql-plain colored"></i> PostgreSQL</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-redis-original colored"></i> Redis</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-react-original colored"></i> React</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-typescript-plain colored"></i> TypeScript</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-tailwindcss-original colored"></i> TailwindCSS</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-jenkins-plain colored"></i> Jenkins</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-azure-plain colored"></i> Azure</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-links">
              <a href="https://drtx2.github.io/copying-amazon/#/" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i> Live Demo</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/DRTX2/ecomerce.git" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Backend Repo</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/DRTX2/copying-amazon" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Frontend Repo</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project">
          <div class="project-image"><img src="/assets/img/in_proccess.png" alt="Medical Clinic Management System" /></div>
          <div class="project-content">
            <h3>Medical Clinic Management System</h3>
            <p>HIPAA-compliant full-stack healthcare system with Clean Architecture backend managing appointments, medical history, and audit trails. Features rate limiting, cache invalidation, and <strong>60% faster medical records retrieval</strong> through 3NF normalization and indexing. Includes responsive React admin dashboard with PDF generation and React Native mobile app (iOS/Android) with push notifications and offline capabilities.</p>
            <div class="technologies">
              <span><i class="devicon-spring-original colored"></i> Spring Boot</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-postgresql-plain colored"></i> PostgreSQL</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-redis-original colored"></i> Redis</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-react-original colored"></i> React</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-react-original colored"></i> React Native</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-tailwindcss-original colored"></i> TailwindCSS</span>
              <span><i><img src="/assets/img/icons8-json-web-token.svg" alt="" /></i> JWT/RBAC</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project">
          <div class="project-image"><img src="/assets/img/maintenance_system.png" alt="SmartNotes Microservices Platform" /></div>
          <div class="project-content">
            <h3>SmartNotes Platform — Microservices Architecture</h3>
            <p>Scalable note-taking platform built with microservices architecture using NestJS and TypeScript. Implements event-driven communication with RabbitMQ, NGINX as API Gateway for routing and authentication, and secure MongoDB/PostgreSQL schemas with proper indexing. Features JWT + RBAC authentication, containerized services with Docker, and comprehensive testing with Jest.</p>
            <div class="technologies">
              <span><i class="devicon-nestjs-original colored"></i> NestJS</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-typescript-plain colored"></i> TypeScript</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-rabbitmq-original colored"></i> RabbitMQ</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-mongodb-original colored"></i> MongoDB</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-postgresql-plain colored"></i> PostgreSQL</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-nginx-original colored"></i> NGINX</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-docker-plain colored"></i> Docker</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project">
          <div class="project-image"><img src="/assets/img/uta_page.jpeg" alt="UTA Elections Page" /></div>
          <div class="project-content">
            <h3>UTA Elections Page</h3>
            <p>A digital platform supporting Dr. Mary Cruz Lascano's 2024-2028 rectorial campaign at the Technical University of Ambato. It informs and connects stakeholders with campaign details, proposals, events, news, and real-time statistics. Built with Laravel, Bootstrap, and MySQL, it ensures functionality and modern design.</p>
            <div class="technologies">
              <span><i class="devicon-laravel-original colored"></i> Laravel</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-javascript-plain colored"></i> JavaScript</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-bootstrap-plain colored"></i> Bootstrap</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-mysql-original colored"></i> MySQL</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-links">
              <a href="https://gitlab.com/personalprojects5531442/manejo-proyecto/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Repository</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project">
          <div class="project-image"><img src="/assets/img/blog.jpeg" alt="My Creative Portfolio" /></div>
          <div class="project-content">
            <h3>My Creative Portfolio</h3>
            <p>My Creative Portfolio is an interactive platform for creating and customizing personal portfolios. It allows users to showcase work professionally, manage projects, and engage with a creative community through comments and collaboration.</p>
            <div class="technologies">
              <span><i class="devicon-php-plain colored"></i> PHP</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-javascript-plain colored"></i> JavaScript</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-axios-plain colored"></i> Axios</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-mysql-original colored"></i> MySQL</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-bootstrap-plain colored"></i> Bootstrap</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-links">
              <a href="https://github.com/DRTX2/proyecto-mds.git" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Repository</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project">
          <div class="project-image"><img src="/assets/img/capibara.jpeg" alt="Capigochi" /></div>
          <div class="project-content">
            <h3>Capigochi</h3>
            <p>Capigochi is an interactive app inspired by Tamagotchis, where users take care of a virtual pet by managing stats such as hunger, energy, and joy. Actions like feeding or playing affect the pet's well-being, and players can restart if its life reaches zero. For this project, I implemented design patterns such as Observer, Factory, Strategy, and Singleton.</p>
            <div class="technologies">
              <span><i class="devicon-java-plain colored"></i> Java</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-mysql-original colored"></i> MySQL</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-links">
              <a href="https://github.com/DRTX2/Capigochi" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Repository</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project">
          <div class="project-image"><img src="/assets/img/consulting-firm.avif" alt="Consulting firm" /></div>
          <div class="project-content">
            <h3>Web Agency</h3>
            <p>A responsive website built with Bootstrap, replicating a professional web agency's platform. This project showcases service packages for web development, highlighting modern design, usability, and mobile-first responsiveness.</p>
            <div class="technologies">
              <span><i class="devicon-javascript-plain colored"></i> JavaScript</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-html5-plain colored"></i> HTML</span>
              <span><i class="devicon-bootstrap-plain colored"></i> Bootstrap</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-links">
              <a href="https://drtx2.github.io/consulting-firm/" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i> Live Site</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/DRTX2/consulting-firm/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-github"></i> Repository</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-cta" id="contact">
      <div class="cta-container">
        <h2>Let's Work <span class="enfasis-title">Together</span></h2>
        <p class="cta-subtitle">I'm always interested in hearing about new projects and opportunities. Whether you need a full-stack solution, backend architecture, or frontend excellence, let's create something amazing together.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/david-manjarres-quintero-056823211/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-button primary" aria-label="Connect with me on LinkedIn">
            <i class="devicon-linkedin-plain" aria-hidden="true"></i> Connect on LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/DRTX2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-button secondary" aria-label="View my projects on GitHub">
            <i class="devicon-github-original" aria-hidden="true"></i> View GitHub
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:davidmanjarres2004@gmail.com" class="cta-button secondary" aria-label="Send me an email">
            <i class="fas fa-envelope" aria-hidden="true"></i> Email Me
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-stats">
          <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-number">2+</span><span class="stat-label">Years Experience</span></div>
          <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-number">10+</span><span class="stat-label">Projects Delivered</span></div>
          <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-number">5K+</span><span class="stat-label">Users Served</span></div>
          <div class="stat-item"><span class="stat-number">90%+</span><span class="stat-label">Test Coverage</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
